com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.engine.service

Class DynamicStickyService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.Service
          • com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.engine.service.DynamicStickyService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DynamicEngine

    public abstract class DynamicStickyService
extends android.app.Service
    Sticky service which will restart automatically if killed by the system.

    Useful in low RAM or similar situations where we need to run the service continuously in the background.
